{
  "texts": [
    "Sign-to-text translationWe provide the function to look up the corresponding meanings based on Auslan gloss inputs.",
    "To support this, we first train a model for sign language detection and recognition using deep learning techniques.",
    "This enables us to quickly determine whether a person is using sign language and more accurately translate the performed signs.",
    "We deploy this model on a cloud server, enabling the APP to perform translations seamlessly without hardware constraints.As illustrated in Fig. 2, when the recording camera is activated, our sign language detection model starts operating.",
    "Once the user's initiation of signing is detected, our Auslan gloss recogniser further recognises the current video input and attempts to translate it into an English word."
  ]
}